Baptswap.description: Baptswap is a Decentralized Exchange (DEX) bringing support for fee-on-transfer solutions within a MOVE-based blockchain environment.
Baptswap.content: Baptswap is a decentralized exchange (DEX) operating on the Aptos Network, enabling peer-to-peer cryptocurrency exchanges without the need for trusted intermediaries. Baptswap it the first DEX to introduce the fee-on-transfer model to Aptos, enabling teams to apply a fee on each transfer of their token. These fees can be allocated towards various purposes based on each individual team's needs and financial model. Baptswap uses an automated market maker (AMM) model, where users can trade against a liquidity pool of two assets, rather than an order book of buy and sell orders. Liquidity providers can earn fees by depositing their tokens into the pool, and traders can swap any token pair supported by the protocol. Baptswap handles the price calculations and slippage adjustments automatically, making trading fast and simple. Baptswap is leveraging the advantages of the Aptos Network and the MOVE language, through a user-friendly and innovative DEX experience for the DeFi users on Aptos.

Official link: https://linktr.ee/avitusxyz  Features: Avitus, is a novel perpetual futures infrastructure protocol:  - allows any asset to be used as collateral (LSTs, NFTs, ERC20, etc). - enables creation & launch of perpetual futures market with ease. - unlocks deep liquidity for perpetual futures with ever-growing list of assets. - allows multiple market designs based on requirements of market creator. - engineered to adapt to new trends or hypothesis. - built from ground-up to democratize perpetual futures markets. - offers perpetual futures and swap markets by default. - created with above-industry standard risk management mechanisms. - powered by robust tamper-proof, fault-proof & outlier proof hybrid oracle delivered by combination of on-chain & real-world sources. - adapts a hybrid funding mechanism to maintain sustainability of markets. - provides non-custodian trade execution to end-users. - easily deployable across different chains. - scale DeFi with massive liquidity and unlimited listings towards more liquid futures.  Avitus differentiates itself all from other perp DEXes in the sense that it is community-driven and users are in control similar to how Uniswap works. This allows:  1. Anyone to launch their own perpetual futures market of their own token (benefical to the project tokens to attract traders) and/or  2. Anyone to launch perpetual futures market using their own tokens (benefits the ecosystem as it increase token utility for all tokens in the ecosystem)

Ortege AI.description: At Ortege, we have developed an advanced data analytics platform that encompasses a range of innovative products, each tailored to meet the evolving demands of data analysis and intelligence. Ortege AI.content: At Ortege, we have developed an advanced data analytics platform that encompasses a range of innovative products, each tailored to meet the evolving demands of data analysis and intelligence. Our suite of products is designed to harness the power of big data, AI, and real-time analytics, providing users with insightful, data-driven solutions. Here’s an overview of our products: Ortege Studio: This is our flagship data visualization and exploration tool, built upon the robust foundations of Apache Superset. Ortege Studio is engineered to be a strong competitor in the data analytics market, rivaling platforms like Dune and Flipside. It offers users an intuitive interface for creating dynamic dashboards and reports, making data analysis accessible and engaging. Ortege Lakehouse v2: Serving as the backbone of our data infrastructure, Ortege Lakehouse integrates seamlessly with Apache Doris, facilitating efficient data streaming to a RedPanda Kafka endpoint. This data is then ingested into the Lakehouse, ensuring a seamless flow of information and enabling real-time data processing and analytics. This lakehouse architecture is pivotal in handling large-scale data workloads, providing both the flexibility of a data lake and the robustness of a data warehouse. OrtegeGPT: Our cutting-edge Large Language Model (LLM), OrtegeGPT, represents a significant leap in AI-driven analytics. By streaming data in real-time to the Llama LLM, OrtegeGPT can generate insights and answers.  Ortege Notebooks: This allows our customers to run Python and R code against our datasets in Lakehouse SPRAY: This term encapsulates the entire technological ecosystem that underpins all Ortege products.  In summary, at Ortege AI, we're not just building tools; we're crafting a comprehensive data analytics ecosystem that empowers users to unlock the full potential of their data, from visualization and exploration to AI-driven insights and research.

Sign Protocol.description: Sign Protocol is an omni-chain attestation protocol, enabling users to freely attest and verify any information on-chain.
Sign Protocol.content: Every day, we are faced with a miscellany of claims and assertions made by various entities in the real world and on the web that we have to work with. Typically, we resort to the classic trust assumptions and relationships of the systems we operate in, such as an entity being honest, or an authority, to establish confirmation of such claims. In the rapidly evolving world, and web, it is becoming less efficient to simply trust and more crucial to verify everything.  Sign Protocol offers a suite of tools, infrastructure, and standards to create a future where all claims and assertions on the web and the world around us are driven by verifiable attestations. It does this by leveraging modern technologies, such as decentralized blockchains and data storage solutions, along with novel techniques such as the use of zero-knowledge cryptography and digital signatures.

Babylon.content: Babylon is a blockchain project that designs security sharing protocols for the decentralized world, founded in 2022 by Stanford Professor David Tse and Dr. Fisher Yu. Professor Tse is a member of the U.S. Academy of Engineering. He is renowned as the inventor of the legendary proportional-fair scheduling algorithm for wireless communications, and is the recipient of prestigious awards such as the IEEE Claude E. Shannon Award and the IEEE Richard W. Hamming Medal. The project is led by a team of consensus protocol researchers and experienced layer 1 engineers from around the world. Babylon's mission is to scale Bitcoin to secure the decentralized world. To achieve this, Babylon utilizes the three primary facets of Bitcoin: its asset, its reliable timestamping service, and its most censorship-resistant blockspace in the world. To leverage these facets, Babylon is developing three innovative security-sharing protocols: Bitcoin Staking Protocol, Bitcoin Timestamping Protocol, and Bitcoin Data Availability Protocol. Through these pioneering protocols, Babylon envisions a more secure and decentralized future.

Lucia Protocol.description: Lucia Protocol is a revolutionalry lending and borrowing platform that empowers individuals and startup enterprise to obtain credit quickly and easily.
Lucia Protocol.content: Lucia Protocol is a non-custodial lending and borrowing protocol, with the primary goal of providing both individuals and startups with seamless access to credit within a framework built on trust. At its core, Lucia revolutionizes the lending landscape by offering borrowers an unparalleled chance to secure credit, all backed by a meticulous credit assessment process that spans both on-chain and off-chain data sources. This credit is designed to offer essential support for managing day-to-day and operational expenses, contributing to financial stability.
Lucia Protocol.slug: Transforming the Collateral Landscape with User-Centric Insights

Jackal.content: Bring Jackal's actually decentralized storage to your blockchain or dApp, all with a simple smart contract call. No Big Cloud middleman. No central points of failure. No platform risk. No problems.

Shuriken.description: Multichain trading suite designed to simplify and enhance your DeFi experience.
Shuriken.content: Shuriken is a comprehensive DeFi trading suite, offering a range of advanced trading applications. Users gain quick and seamless access to bridging, trading, sniping, and advanced orders from any device, providing a competitive edge in any Web3 market.

Movewiffrens.description: Connect, engage, and grow in the Movement ecosystem with our SocialFi platform.
Movewiffrens.content: Welcome to Movewiffrens, a pioneering SocialFi platform designed to enhance the Movement ecosystem. Our mission is to connect users and creators through secure, autonomous, and inclusive digital experiences. Movewiffrens offers diverse content, personalized profiles, and robust community engagement. By integrating a monetization model and seamless accessibility via Telegram mini-app, we empower a vibrant and interactive community. Join us and be part of a movement that values contribution and innovation!

Gmover.description: Gmover is a GameFi Project built on Movement Network.
Gmover.content: Welcome to Gmover. The Movement community will constantly earn by having fun with Gmover, playing games, staking their NFTs, and doing Tasks. The best way to earn while having fun is Gmover. In the Gmover game, each user has 1 land registered on the onchain. However, this Land is barren at first. Users can turn their land into a special area by using farming tools.
